metadata.name: Suns Journey
metadata.description:
A journey through environment and form led by playful dynamics. 

Equal split between HAGAR, Art Aid and myself.

Hagar is a well-established non-government international organization dedicated to the recovery of women and children who have endured extreme abuses. They work to see communities free and healed from the trauma of human trafficking, slavery and abuse.

Custom analogue sound design by Lumana.

6K Version available upon request by owner.
